### âœ… Checklist Template (Printable)

**Pro Se Survival Checklist**

- [ ]  Received withdrawal notice from court docket
- [ ]  Collected all filings and exhibits
- [ ]  Preserved evidence with metadata
- [ ]  Filed Notice of Appearance Pro Se
- [ ]  Updated contact info with court
- [ ]  Created calendar of deadlines
- [ ]  Joined coalition support channels
- [ ]  Prepared filing templates
- [ ]  Practiced stress management rituals

